         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>l. 2, <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΤΡΙΩΝ</foreign> might possibly the end of a word begun in l.3.</p>
            <p>ll. 2-3, <foreign xml:lang="grc">οἰκοδομή<unclear reason="damage">μ</unclear>
                  <supplied reason="lost">ατ</supplied>α</foreign> would be possible, but for <foreign xml:lang="grc">περιοικοδομή<unclear reason="damage">μ</unclear>ατα</foreign> in a theatrical context see O.A.W. Dilke, MH 5 (1948), 64 (SEG)</p>
            <p>l.6, cf <foreign xml:lang="grc">καταστεγάζω</foreign>, L.B. Holland, AJA 54 (1950), 343-6 (SEG)</p>
